0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"我都有生<br />\n但冇膿頭點唧？<br />\n粒野唔係表面嫁wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892d09f7e6d8d4db4c26de54b6eed349ba95a69a","tid":808772,"uid":66108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:11:27.000Z","msg":"我都間唔中有生出黎<br />\n早一兩年有一次 頂佢唔順 係咁起勢搓佢<br />\n搞搞下漲到仆街 hi到都痛 之後忍痛吱佢 啲膿爆出黎嗰一幕真係畢生難忙"},{"pid":"0d6a792cd2ac77d5e55004cfc3707d42f9c9433b","tid":808772,"uid":27162,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f49cbb2c2ad147a6babede6cdfc8dadf5ae62f8","tid":808772,"uid":151664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"係暗瘡 禁吓粒野個位，強行唧爆佢。<br />\n一定有濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次唧完都好爽"},{"pid":"08dfd55aa67ffb5902912aea7d9c5a2f64f8c7fc","tid":808772,"uid":63553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:26:20.000Z","msg":"認真 因為熱氣"},{"pid":"7f83ff4a07b62ae538d262184ce01d9cdaf1b786","tid":808772,"uid":126845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:32:26.000Z","msg":"我有時碌鳩都會生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係可以唧粒野出黎<br />\n係咪正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a50a79fe5c2b5a975414537133b8a283242765","tid":808772,"uid":16120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"暗瘡積積埋埋變粉瘤<br />\n其實冇乜野 係周不時會發炎 痛 麻煩<br />\n要小手術切走入面泡野先斷尾<br />\n但切完唔保證唔會復發"},{"pid":"ead32b039b224de86570b04f4ee204908903ee0f","tid":808772,"uid":42759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:42:36.000Z","msg":"我都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ec3f0db277d85ae37c15211d0a66e3e9df8ff5","tid":808772,"uid":3031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:52:34.000Z","msg":"我之前都有, 我都覺得會唔會係穿耳窿所以有<br />\n5年前穿完之後間中就有, 試過掂下都痛, 但係隔一個禮拜自己就退, 之後又再生 好似有周期咁<br />\n<br />\n但係自從今年年頭唔再要個窿, 等佢埋左口之後去到今日為止, 完全無再生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4d78a10f07714a9aeb756c159bc2b7f12af643","tid":808772,"uid":20455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:55:48.000Z","msg":"屌 我都有 原來咁多人都咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我嗰粒已經持續左成年<br />\n有時唧完 過一排又生返 好似暗瘡咁"},{"pid":"434c8f54f9a6949000553b8662091ffc1a86bc1e","tid":808772,"uid":45228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:12:52.000Z","msg":"唔會痛，但有時會有但都會消失變細<br />\n求解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc473dd2bf68bb6128ef7ad812d7a5bd791fe1e7","tid":808772,"uid":203257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:17:49.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\n真心想知係咩黎"},{"pid":"1b5c8893a553ef22e2805020452c55fe1c4612f5","tid":808772,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:20:58.000Z","msg":"我都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c64d9d6f58d89f0b4ba1138904e82883ad0ab81","tid":808772,"uid":109117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:27:40.000Z","msg":"我都有<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"ca2d484588653e6506724df3c3d117ec99687802","tid":808772,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11af293119f687f81354f169bc5e2204e03eac27","tid":80877